So I want to have the text section on the left side. It will be an texta area where we will be able to enter text. The component will output an onChange property that will fire onKeyUp. 

On the right side we will have the visualizer. Right now the visualizer will only work for the word "apple". For any other word, other then apple, the visualizer will say -- Unknown concept: "whatever is written in the textarea that is not apple" (Currently `apple` is the only visualized concept)

Next inside the visualizer if "apple" is present (and only "apple") then we want to show a rendering tth
